## Plan: EWA Analyzer V2 — Phase-by-Phase Implementation

**TL;DR:** 6 implementation phases (Phase 0 sets foundations, Phases 1–5 are sequential, Phase 6 is frontend). Each phase is independently verifiable before moving to the next.

